00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:36.260
 Parody songs are a good example of contrafacts, just like translations. 

00:00:36.260 --> 00:00:39.800
 But unlike parodies, translations of songs often give the wrong impression 

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:41.980
