00:01:11.969 --> 00:01:14.509
 And this song is not the only case where this happens. 

00:01:14.509 --> 00:01:16.439
 With every translation of a song, 

00:01:16.439 --> 00:01:20.659
 there is a conflict between the meaning of the text and the way it sounds when it is pronounced. 

00:01:20.659 --> 00:01:24.939
 If you were to translate a song purely based on meaning, 

00:01:24.939 --> 00:01:28.680
