00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:58.340
 That was Whitney Houston. 

00:02:58.349 --> 00:03:00.969
 And other languages, such as German or Polish, 

00:03:00.969 --> 00:03:03.510
 Are more suitable for syllabic singing. 

00:03:03.510 --> 00:03:06.000
 Where you have a note per vowel. 

00:03:06.700 --> 00:03:09.160
 ♫ Freude schöner Götterfunken 

00:03:09.160 --> 00:03:12.120
